bpmn-diagram

title Online Order Fulfillment

Customer [color: black] {
  Need product [type: event]
  Place order [type: activity, icon: shopping-cart]
  Shipment received [type: event, icon: mail]
  Order completed [type: event]
}

Online Store {
  Sales {
    Verify payment [type: activity, icon: credit-card]
    Payment approved? [type: gateway, icon: x]
    Generate pick list [type: activity, icon: list]
  }
  Warehouse {
    Pick items [type: activity, icon: box]
    Pack & label shipment [type: activity, icon: package]
    Ship order [type: activity, icon: truck]
    Shipped [type: event]
  }
}

Need product > Place order
Place order --> Verify payment : Order
Verify payment > Payment approved?
Payment approved? > Generate pick list : Yes
Payment approved? --> Order completed : Payment declined
Generate pick list --> Pick items : Pick list
Pick items > Pack & label shipment
Pack & label shipment > Ship order
Place order > Shipment received
Ship order --> Shipment received : Shipment
Ship order > Shipped
Shipment received > Order completed
